You took this from the naming policy, I was mearly pointing out that the term &quot;Popular Media&quot; has NOTHING to do with the popularity of the author.  The book is a published piece of literature, therefore, part of popular media..  even if only 2 people read it.  That was the point I was trying to make<br>
